import React, { useState } from 'react';

import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';

import {BrowserRouter, Route, Link, Switch} from 'react-router-dom'

import HeaderName from './component/HeaderName'
import HeaderNav from './component/HeaderNav'
import HomePage from './component/Home'
import WorkPage from './component/Works'
import ResumePage from './component/Resume'
import Footer from './component/Foot'

import './App.css';


const App = () => (
  <Container fluid style={{background:"black"}}>
    <BrowserRouter>
    <Row style={{height:"15vh"}}>
      <Col style={{borderColor:"white"}} xs={4}>
        <HeaderName/>
      </Col>
      <Col style={{borderColor:"white",justifyContent:"center",alignItems:"center"}} xs={8}>
        <HeaderNav />
      </Col>
    </Row>
    
    <Switch>
      <Route path="/home/" component={HomePage} />
      <Route path="/works/" component={WorkPage} />
      <Route path="/resume/" component={ResumePage} />
    </Switch>
    
    <Row style={{height:"5vh", bottom:0, textAlign:"center", justifyContent:"center"}}>
      <Footer />
    </Row>
    </BrowserRouter>
  </Container>
);

export default App;
